1. Navigated into the alx-intermediate-frontend repository.

2. Created a new directory called 0x03-sass_scss:
   mkdir 0x03-sass_scss
   cd 0x03-sass_scss

3. Installed nvm using the command:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

4. Exited and reopened the terminal.

5. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using:
   nvm install 20.16
   nvm use 20.16

6. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using:
   npm install sass -v 3.7.4
